Package com.ibm.team.repository.common.query

Interface Summary
IDataField Data fields represent descriptions of the columnar data returned from data queries.
IDataQuery a data query is a type of query used for retrieving fields of related items, or values computed by aggregate or scalar functions.
IDataQueryPage Represents the definition of a query page for data queries.
IDataRow Represents a row of data from a data query result.
IDataRow.Factory  
IDataTypes Enumeration interface that defines int constants corresponding to all data query field types.
IItemQuery an item query is a type of query used for retrieving the handles of all items matching a set of filter criteria.
IItemQueryPage Represents the definition of a query page for item queries.
IQuery Represents a structured query over items in the Jazz repository.
IQueryPage Represents the abstract definition of a paged query result.
IQueryResult  
IScored  
ITextQueryPage Represents the definition of a query page for text queries.
 

Class Summary
IQuery.Factory internal use only
 

Exception Summary
QueryException
